videos.description: D'Juan Hines forces Anthony Miller to fumble the ball as Houston recovers with good field position.
videos.headline: Cougars force first turnover

videos.description: Dillon Birden muscles in a 1-yard touchdown run to give Houston the lead in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Birden punches in Houston TD

videos.description: Duke Catalon pushes his way into the end zone for a 4-yard touchdown to give the Cougars a two-touchdown lead.
videos.headline: Catalon wills his way into the end zone

videos.description: Garrett Davis intercepts Riley Ferguson's pass and returns 58 yards to Memphis' 16-yard line.
videos.headline: Houston picks off Ferguson

videos.description: Mike Norvell said Memphis hasn't played well offensively but he expects his team to respond in the second half.
videos.headline: Norvell has 'total faith' in how Memphis will respond in second half

videos.description: Coach Major Applewhite is pleased with the way Houston played in the first half and he preached to his team that they need to play a full 60 minutes.
videos.headline: Houston needs to keep momentum from first half

videos.description: Tigers running back Patrick Taylor Jr.'s 2-yard run on Memphis' first drive in the second half closes the gap to 17-7.
videos.headline: Taylor Jr. bullies his way into the end zone for first Memphis TD

videos.description: Duke Catalon and the Houston offense responds to Memphis' touchdown with a 1-yard touchdown run on the ensuing driving.
videos.headline: Houston answers with short TD run

videos.description: Dillon Birden runs to the edge for a 40-yard run to the Memphis 35-yard line.
videos.headline: Birden runs to the outside for 40 yards

videos.description: Duke Catalon gets his third touchdown with a 1-yard run to give Houston a 31-14 lead.
videos.headline: Catalon scores third TD

videos.description: Memphis' Patrick Taylor Jr. sprints into the end zone for a 9-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Tigers score on three plays

videos.description: Tito Windham strips sacks Kyle Postma and Memphis recovers.
videos.headline: Postma gets stripped sacked, Memphis recovers

videos.description: Patrick Taylor rushes into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown run to bring the Tigers within three points.
videos.headline: Memphis takes advantage of Houston turnover

videos.description: Kyle Postma connects with Steven Dunbar for an 8-yard touchdown to give Houston a two possession lead late in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Houston protects lead with late fourth-quarter TD

videos.description: Patrick Taylor Jr.'s 5-yard touchdown run puts Memphis within a field goal.
videos.headline: Taylor Jr. scores fourth TD as Memphis pulls within three

videos.description: Sean Dykes catches a 21-yard touchdown pass from Riley Ferguson to give Memphis the lead for the first time with under two minutes to play.
videos.headline: Dykes scores go-ahead touchdown for Memphis

videos.description: Terrell Carter the ball loose from Kyle Postma as Memphis recovers late in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Memphis forces another Houston fumble

videos.description: Terrell Carter completes Memphis' come-from-behind win with a late interception to seal the win for the Tigers.
videos.headline: Memphis seals game with INT

videos.description: Memphis coach Mike Norvell said he couldn't be more proud of the way his team responded in the second half with 42 points after being held scoreless in the first half.
videos.headline: Norvell: 'It wasn't pretty at all times'

videos.description: Memphis quarterback Riley Ferguson says Memphis came out and executed to their full potential in the second half.
videos.headline: Ferguson on comeback win: 'It was a roller coaster'

videos.description: Memphis receiver Anthony Miller says Memphis never doubted that they would win.
videos.headline: Miller: 'We knew we could win'

videos.description: Andre Ware breaks down how Memphis turned it around in the second half to beat Houston after trailing 17-0 at halftime.
videos.headline: Ware: Riley Ferguson transformed into finisher in second half
